# Shell scripts, git hooks and Node hook-scripts MUST stay LF so they execute in
# bash (CI is ubuntu) and via git hooks regardless of the checkout platform.
# Without this, a Windows checkout rewrites them to CRLF and bash/`grep -P` based
# scripts misbehave locally.
*.sh        text eol=lf
*.mjs       text eol=lf
.husky/**   text eol=lf
